/* GIIIFT — full-face "panel wrap" library for the box engine.
 *
 * Each entry: id -> { name, group, fields?, svg }
 *   group  : "front" — hero face with a centrepiece · "side" — quieter paired wrap
 *   fields : editable text slots — [{ key, label, value, max }]. The SVG contains
 *            {{key}} tokens; the engine substitutes them with the user's text WITHOUT
 *            touching the surrounding <text> styling, so edits stay "in the panel's style".
 *   svg    : self-contained flat SVG (viewBox 0 0 100 100, preserveAspectRatio="none",
 *            unique internal ids so several panels can coexist in one document).
 *
 * Load BEFORE box-engine.js. Authored in-repo (trusted) → inlined as-is.
 */
